      <? $var ?> looks too like Text::MicroTemplate
    - render() requires a file name:
        my $tx = Text::Xslate->new( file => [qw(foo.tx bar.tx)] );
        print $tx->render('foo.tx', \%vars);
        print $tx->render('bar.tx', \%vars);

